        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 57 of a 12-week money program. The script targets the scarcity-pie belief: the idea that wealth is finite and that every gain someone else makes is ground you can't reach. The reframe moves toward wealth as an expanding current, one that does not run out when it flows.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
